= StatusNet (formerly Laconica[4]) is a FLOSS microblogging  server written in PHP that implements the OStatus standard for interoperation between installations. While offering functionality similar to Twitter, StatusNet seeks to provide the potential for open, inter-service and distributed communications between microblogging communities. Enterprises and individuals can install and control their own services and data [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/StatusNet]

URL = http://status.net/


